---
---

<div id="como-funciona" class="exp-section">
  <div class="exp-container">

    <div class="exp-header">
      <div class="exp-headline-col">
        <h2 class="exp-headline reveal">
          Experiencia que crece<br />con tu escala.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-body-col reveal stagger-2">
        <p class="exp-body">
          Desde escanear tu constancia hasta tener tu CFDI válido en menos de dos minutos. Sin contadores, sin instalaciones, sin drama.
        </p>
        <div class="exp-trust">
          <div class="exp-trust-item">
            <div class="exp-trust-icon" style="background: var(--kipo-gradient);">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span>SAT autorizado</span>
          </div>
          <span class="exp-trust-sep" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <div class="exp-trust-item">
            <div class="exp-trust-icon" style="background-color: #0EA5E9;">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span>FacturAPI · PAC certificado</span>
          </div>
          <span class="exp-trust-sep" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <div class="exp-trust-item">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
            <span>Timbrado en segundos</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="exp-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="exp-steps">

      <div class="exp-step reveal stagger-1">
        <div class="exp-step-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/>
            <path d="M8 6h1M8 9h1M8 12h1"/>
            <path d="M12 6h4M12 9h4M12 12h4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="exp-step-title">Escanea tu constancia</h3>
        <p class="exp-step-body">Sube el PDF del SAT con tu RFC. Llenamos el resto solos — régimen, domicilio, nombre fiscal.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="exp-step-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="exp-step reveal stagger-2">
        <div class="exp-step-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/>
            <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/>
            <polyline points="9 15 11 17 15 13"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="exp-step-title">Crea tu factura</h3>
        <p class="exp-step-body">Agrega concepto, monto y datos de tu cliente. IVA calculado automáticamente según tu régimen fiscal.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="exp-step-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="exp-step reveal stagger-3">
        <div class="exp-step-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="exp-step-title">Timbra y cobra</h3>
        <p class="exp-step-body">CFDI 4.0 válido ante el SAT en segundos. Envía por WhatsApp, correo o descarga el PDF y XML.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .exp-section {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .exp-container {
    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .exp-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .exp-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.25rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--text-strong);
    text-wrap: balance;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .exp-body-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .exp-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-body);
    max-width: 44ch;
    text-wrap: pretty;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .exp-trust {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem 0.875rem;
  }

  .exp-trust-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.375rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .exp-trust-icon {
    width: 1.375rem;
    height: 1.375rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .exp-trust-sep {
    color: var(--border-subtle);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .exp-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border-subtle);
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* ── Steps: 3-col ── */
  .exp-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 0 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .exp-step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.625rem;
  }

  .exp-step-icon {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .exp-step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-strong);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .exp-step-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--text-body);
    max-width: 24ch;
    text-wrap: pretty;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .exp-step-divider {
    width: 1px;
    background: var(--border-subtle);
    align-self: stretch;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .exp-section {
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .exp-header {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .exp-headline {
      font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 6vw, 2.5rem);
    }

    .exp-body-col {
      align-items: center;
    }

    .exp-trust {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .exp-steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .exp-step {
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .exp-step-body {
      max-width: unset;
    }

    .exp-step-divider {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
